WEBVTT

00:48.120 --> 00:58.120
First three minutes are without sound.

01:17.190 --> 01:27.190
The Left Side - Problems of the Subconscious

01:28.220 --> 01:38.220
May 13th, 1982, Christchurch Hove, Brighton, England

02:32.100 --> 02:34.120
Good conditionings.

02:36.010 --> 02:40.200
In the way, in the same way, you can have good habits

02:41.230 --> 02:45.170
and bad habits.

03:24.230 --> 03:26.140
If habits inhibit or

03:26.230 --> 03:29.010
obstruct your ascent,

03:31.210 --> 03:38.020
they also can help to stabilize you.

03:45.040 --> 03:49.040
The conditioning comes to you from the matter

03:49.150 --> 03:52.230
with which we are dealing every day.

03:53.230 --> 03:59.020
When a human being sees the matter, he aggressor it and

03:59.100 --> 04:04.010
he wants to use that matter for his own purpose.

04:04.100 --> 04:08.240
He changes the forms of the matter for his own purpose.

04:09.070 --> 04:12.210
He starts getting used to matter

04:14.040 --> 04:20.130
as comfort, or as a help or a guide in life.

04:21.210 --> 04:24.240
The more you start depending on matter,

04:25.060 --> 04:28.100
the more your spontaneity is finished,

04:28.180 --> 04:32.110
because you’re dealing with the dead.

04:35.000 --> 04:38.180
Matter, when it is dead, then only we deal with it.

04:39.010 --> 04:43.180
When it is living we are not so much bothered about it.

04:44.030 --> 04:49.000
So the deadness of that matter settles within us when

04:49.070 --> 04:54.240
we start using that matter for our purpose.

04:55.140 --> 04:58.170
But how are we to otherwise exist? Is the question

04:59.060 --> 05:02.050
people can ask. If God has given us this material things

05:02.160 --> 05:04.200
and this matter to be used,

05:05.050 --> 05:07.240
are we not supposed to use them?

05:08.100 --> 05:13.160
And are we not supposed to enjoy them?

05:13.230 --> 05:17.220
But we don’t enjoy. We …

05:18.140 --> 05:22.130
before Realization you cannot enjoy any matter.

05:22.230 --> 05:26.140
You can only form a habit and may become

05:26.210 --> 05:30.100
a slave of that matter, before Realization.

05:30.220 --> 05:35.180
It’s a principle of, fundamental principle of economics

05:36.000 --> 05:39.090
that wants in general are never satiable.

05:39.170 --> 05:42.190
Means today you want to buy something like a carpet.

05:43.010 --> 05:45.030
All right, you bought it.

05:45.180 --> 05:49.000
So now that carpet becames a headache, because it’s

05:49.000 --> 05:52.040
your possession, you have to look after it.

05:52.170 --> 05:55.140
You have to insure it, you have to worry about it that it

05:56.000 --> 05:59.040
doesn’t get spoiled, first of all.

05:59.180 --> 06:02.010
And secondly you really get

06:02.110 --> 06:06.020
into another mood of buying something else.

06:06.020 --> 06:08.180
Now you have bought the carpet, finished.

06:09.040 --> 06:10.120
Then you have to have something else, then you have to

06:10.210 --> 06:11.200
have something else,

06:12.030 --> 06:13.040
then you have to have something else.

06:13.150 --> 06:18.110
So it does not satiate you; it does not give you the joy.

06:20.180 --> 06:22.220
Matter can never give you joy.

06:23.050 --> 06:25.210
It’s the Spirit that gives you joy.

06:26.200 --> 06:28.190
And when the ascent takes place,

06:29.040 --> 06:33.130
when you become the Spirit, then matter takes another

06:33.240 --> 06:35.200
value system within ourselves,

06:36.040 --> 06:40.150
the value system of matter is very different.

06:41.040 --> 06:43.130
As I’m sure Jason must have told you that

06:43.240 --> 06:45.180
when you get your Realization,

06:46.150 --> 06:50.030
then you start feeling the Cool Breeze in the hand.

06:53.120 --> 06:55.040
In relationship to matter

06:55.170 --> 06:59.040
it’s very helpful to be a realized soul,

06:59.210 --> 07:04.020
because immediately you know

07:04.160 --> 07:08.020
what is good for you and what is bad for you.

07:08.100 --> 07:12.060
For example, you eat something that’s not good for you.

07:12.060 --> 07:14.000
Immediately you’ll lose your vibrations

07:14.110 --> 07:15.150
and will become hot.

07:16.020 --> 07:18.150
Even looking at it, it may happen.

07:19.010 --> 07:21.230
You want to sit on a chair on which somebody who is a

07:22.070 --> 07:24.170
very wrong type of a person has sat,

07:25.030 --> 07:26.230
immediately you’ll feel, “Oh, something wrong

07:27.060 --> 07:29.100
in this place.” With your vibrations,

07:29.200 --> 07:34.130
which is a definite thing, an absolute thing.

07:36.030 --> 07:39.060
And this conditioning can only be over –

07:39.060 --> 07:43.050
these habits can be overcome only if you become the Spirit,

07:43.190 --> 07:48.170
because Spirit is always dominated by the matter.

07:49.020 --> 07:52.000
And the Spirit has to overcome that domination of the matter.

07:54.230 --> 07:58.230
Actually, Spirit cannot be dominated by anything.

07:59.090 --> 08:02.240
But what I mean is that it is covered, like the sun can be

08:03.090 --> 08:06.240
covered with clouds.

08:06.240 --> 08:09.230
In the same way all our domination,

08:10.190 --> 08:17.110
or we can say all our enslavement of the matter,

08:17.110 --> 08:20.090
makes us dominate our Spirit in the sense that

08:20.230 --> 08:23.040
we cover it up. The clouds are there,

08:23.040 --> 08:25.000
we can’t see the Spirit. We can’t feel It.

08:25.130 --> 08:28.150
The spontaneity which is the beauty of the Spirit

08:28.220 --> 08:30.240
we do not feel, in a person.

08:31.090 --> 08:34.040
So, in judging a person, what do we judge?

08:34.140 --> 08:37.060
How that person looks, what dress he’s wearing,

08:37.180 --> 08:40.050
how he walks. What are his formal ways,

08:40.130 --> 08:42.160
does he know how to say “Thank you”, “Sorry” or not.

08:43.010 --> 08:45.070
You see? All these things impress us very much.

08:45.180 --> 08:49.200
What sort of a car he has, what sort of a house he has.

08:50.050 --> 08:56.200
Maybe we may miss, we may miss a saint.

08:57.100 --> 08:59.140
We may miss Christ again

08:59.230 --> 09:02.210
because He was a carpenter’s son.

09:03.070 --> 09:06.030
How are we to know who is Christ?

09:06.110 --> 09:11.110
Is there any way of finding out who is Christ?

09:11.190 --> 09:13.210
Many people are now talking “Christ is going to come,

09:14.090 --> 09:15.170
He’s going to come on the television.”

09:16.020 --> 09:19.140
You can put up anyone there as Christ.

09:19.220 --> 09:22.040
How are we going to make it out?

09:22.140 --> 09:25.060
By His dress or by some sort of a thing they have done?

09:25.150 --> 09:29.040
Most of the paintings of Christ and most of His statues

09:29.140 --> 09:31.230
that I’ve seen are no where near Christ,

09:32.080 --> 09:34.020
no where near Christ, you see.

09:34.120 --> 09:37.230
They are horrid things. I don’t know what are they.

09:38.070 --> 09:41.100
So how will you make it out that this is Christ or not?

09:41.190 --> 09:44.080
Or this is some sort of a hokus pokus fellow or some sort

09:44.180 --> 09:49.070
of a person who has come just deliberately to delude us

09:49.150 --> 09:51.210
from reality.

09:52.070 --> 09:55.180
There is no way out, to find out

09:57.020 --> 10:01.140
what is the truth because we are so much used to material

10:01.220 --> 10:03.040
forms that we have.

10:03.200 --> 10:08.200
For example, our idea of art also is in the same way

10:09.080 --> 10:11.110
molded.

10:11.210 --> 10:13.180
We like this kind of art.

10:14.030 --> 10:15.020
If you ask them, “Why?”

10:15.020 --> 10:18.150
“Because, you know, this has this kind of a thing

10:18.230 --> 10:20.060
– harmony” Or maybe,

10:20.170 --> 10:22.170
“this is more proportioned” and all that.

10:23.010 --> 10:26.030
But how do you know?”

10:26.130 --> 10:28.110
You know because you’ve read certain books or maybe

10:28.230 --> 10:34.190
that you have understood from somebody else

10:35.100 --> 10:38.150
that this is art, this is beautiful. I mean, you brand

10:39.000 --> 10:42.070
something as beautiful, but is it really?

10:42.190 --> 10:45.030
If it is beauty, it should be Spirit, because

10:45.160 --> 10:48.040
Spirit is beauty and beauty is Spirit.

10:48.140 --> 10:51.220
So is it, is it beauty? How do you make out

10:52.050 --> 10:55.130
that this art is beautiful or not?

10:55.130 --> 10:58.220
For example, according to all normal ideas of

10:59.040 --> 11:00.090
womanhood, I don’t think

11:00.210 --> 11:03.010
Mona Lisa is a beautiful woman.

11:03.130 --> 11:06.090
I mean, these days you see mosquito-like women are

11:06.170 --> 11:08.040
regarded as beautiful.

11:08.130 --> 11:10.150
So how they call Mona Lisa so beautiful?

11:11.030 --> 11:13.000
What’s going on?

11:13.100 --> 11:15.080
Thousands of people would be assembled to see that

11:15.190 --> 11:18.160
painting. Why? What is that?

11:19.000 --> 11:23.020
Only vibrations will tell you that it emits vibrations.

11:23.120 --> 11:25.120
It appeals to your Spirit without your knowledge.

11:25.220 --> 11:28.140
You’re not aware of it. It appeals to your Spirit.

11:28.230 --> 11:34.090
That’s why universally that painting is appreciated.

11:34.220 --> 11:37.180
But when this conditioning becomes collective,

11:38.020 --> 11:40.000
any such conditioning becomes collective and you

11:40.090 --> 11:45.010
accept, “This is the form that is beauty; this is the form

11:45.010 --> 11:50.120
that is reality; this is the form that is spontaneity”,

11:50.210 --> 11:53.190
then the confusion starts.

11:54.040 --> 11:56.170
The confusion starts at that point,

11:57.010 --> 11:59.130
when it becomes a collective thing.

12:00.090 --> 12:03.050
For example I met some people of some gurus.

12:04.000 --> 12:06.040
And I asked them,

12:06.040 --> 12:08.180
“What makes you think that your guru is truthful,

12:09.000 --> 12:10.030
what has he given you?

12:10.150 --> 12:12.240
He said, “because sitting in my chair I just start jumping

12:13.080 --> 12:18.100
by myself. I don’t do it but it happens, it’s spontaneous.”

12:19.100 --> 12:22.100
And in my presence, the way his body was moving was

12:22.190 --> 12:23.170
so horrifying.

12:24.060 --> 12:27.090
Anybody would have tremendous compassion

12:27.190 --> 12:29.020
and concern for such a person,

12:29.120 --> 12:31.110
that you can’t sit for five minutes straight …

12:31.110 --> 12:33.070
A woman in the audience says: Excuse me, it wasn’t

12:33.210 --> 12:35.080
spontaneous, it was nerve …

12:35.160 --> 12:37.080
Yes, that’s what I’m saying …

12:37.190 --> 12:39.230
Woman: You’re wrong in what You talk.

12:40.050 --> 12:41.060
What?

12:41.170 --> 12:42.220
Woman: About everything

12:42.220 --> 12:44.210
From where do you come?

12:45.060 --> 12:46.130
Woman: Up the road.

12:46.190 --> 12:48.110
That’s it. Better go.

12:49.030 --> 12:51.090
Woman: Don’t worry. I am.

12:51.200 --> 12:55.240
Look at that. She’ll go to the pub now.

12:59.010 --> 13:01.070
Must try to understand the subtleties, you see?

13:01.210 --> 13:03.080
If you are confirmed it what.

13:03.180 --> 13:07.010
Now supposing somebody starts jumping in the thing.

13:07.120 --> 13:09.200
As she says it’s true – nerves.

13:10.080 --> 13:14.030
That means you’re not in control of your nerves, isn’t it?

13:14.120 --> 13:16.240
Don’t you think so? You’re not in control.

13:17.070 --> 13:18.050
You have not controlled.

13:18.200 --> 13:21.160
Spontaneity is a thing which is not the thing that makes

13:22.020 --> 13:23.120
you a slave.

13:23.220 --> 13:25.090
This is the point I’m trying to bring.

13:25.180 --> 13:29.000
It doesn’t; it makes you a master.

13:29.080 --> 13:30.230
Spontaneity must make you a master

13:31.100 --> 13:33.150
and not a slave of anything.

13:34.000 --> 13:35.120
She must have come from TM because TM people

13:35.220 --> 13:38.110
jump like that.

13:38.210 --> 13:41.060
And they end up as epileptic people.

13:41.160 --> 13:42.200
I have cured so many of them.

13:43.040 --> 13:45.140
I don’t know if someone has come from there.

13:45.240 --> 13:51.140
Even the head of their academy in Scotland who –

13:51.220 --> 13:54.120
flying squad academy, as I call it,

13:55.120 --> 13:57.220
where people pay three thousand – now this gentleman

13:58.050 --> 14:01.020
sitting here is one of them who suffered.

14:01.090 --> 14:05.000
When they suffer then they know what it is.

14:05.090 --> 14:07.150
The other day we saw somebody with epilepsy of such

14:07.230 --> 14:10.210
frequency. The poor child, he was hardly twenty-six

14:12.100 --> 14:15.180
years of age, young man, supposed to enjoy his life,

14:16.050 --> 14:21.230
was going into such trauma, you can’t imagine.

14:22.230 --> 14:25.120
And if this is happening to somebody going to a guru,

14:25.200 --> 14:27.040
you paid for it,

14:27.170 --> 14:30.020
how can it be anywhere near Spirit?

14:30.100 --> 14:32.210
This is what I’m trying to tell you, that

14:33.060 --> 14:38.090
Spirit gives you spontaneity in which you are the master.

14:38.190 --> 14:43.090
You are the master of yourself, complete master,

14:43.180 --> 14:47.010
no enslavement of any kind, no habits formation coming.

14:47.110 --> 14:48.190
All habits drop out.

14:48.190 --> 14:51.230
You become so, so spontaneous that I don’t have to tell you.

14:52.070 --> 14:54.070
You just drop out all habits and you become a

14:54.150 --> 14:57.010
master of your self.

14:57.120 --> 14:59.160
That should happen to you.

15:00.010 --> 15:03.230
Instead of that, if you indulge into things which enslave

15:04.060 --> 15:07.010
you, you will like it for awhile

15:07.120 --> 15:08.230
because you can’t help it.

15:09.100 --> 15:12.040
But, if you really sit down you will know that it’s not the

15:12.140 --> 15:14.040
thing that you wanted.

15:14.130 --> 15:16.120
You wanted to be the master of your self.

15:16.240 --> 15:20.050
Now here in this map as we show we have two powers,

15:20.130 --> 15:22.010
left and right powers.

15:22.140 --> 15:26.100
The left power is the power that gives us conditioning –

15:26.190 --> 15:29.160
left side, the subconscious, the collective subconscious.

15:30.010 --> 15:32.030
That gives us the conditioning.

15:32.130 --> 15:35.110
Now, if you try to deny all that, then the right side is

15:35.190 --> 15:37.060
even worse.

15:37.160 --> 15:40.070
It gives us action, but with action we can become very

15:40.160 --> 15:42.150
ego oriented.

15:43.040 --> 15:45.110
So both ways it can be troublesome.

15:45.220 --> 15:47.200
Supposing you say that “All right, I’ll have no

15:48.050 --> 15:50.190
conditioning from anytime. What’s wrong in doing this?

15:51.060 --> 15:52.180
What’s wrong in doing that?”

15:53.100 --> 15:57.190
And if you just move with that idea, with that freedom,

15:58.070 --> 16:00.190
it will be abandonment, it may not be freedom.

16:01.060 --> 16:04.030
Because freedom must have wisdom behind it.

16:04.150 --> 16:05.140
So both the sides,

16:06.000 --> 16:10.030
the movements on both the sides are wrong.

16:10.130 --> 16:11.240
So what is all right?

16:12.090 --> 16:16.200
In the center is not to get conditioned by anything and

16:17.060 --> 16:21.020
not to be ego oriented.

16:21.090 --> 16:23.050
But how to do it is the problem.

16:23.130 --> 16:25.090
The problem is how to do it.

16:25.170 --> 16:31.130
To be spontaneous is to be absolutely free.

16:32.080 --> 16:35.200
Now I would consider these two powers as, say, a brake

16:36.040 --> 16:39.010
and an accelerator in a car.

16:39.090 --> 16:40.220
Now you use both the powers.

16:41.060 --> 16:43.220
You use the brake first, you use the accelerator.

16:44.040 --> 16:46.130
You try to control these two powers.

16:46.130 --> 16:49.140
But, first of all it is difficult to understand

16:49.240 --> 16:51.090
how you can use these powers.

16:51.240 --> 16:53.110
Gradually, with practice you’ll do it.

16:53.200 --> 16:55.060
You know how to drive the car,

16:55.190 --> 16:58.120
you become the good driver.

16:58.190 --> 17:01.010
After becoming the good driver, still

17:01.100 --> 17:04.000
you are not the master of the driving,

17:04.070 --> 17:06.190
but then you become the master.

17:07.040 --> 17:11.180
So, today the master within us, within us is the Spirit.

17:12.020 --> 17:15.190
But before Realization, you are not the master

17:16.070 --> 17:20.220
because the master has not come in our conscious mind.

17:21.060 --> 17:23.140
It is not expressing in our conscious mind.

17:24.030 --> 17:31.070
In the sense that we are not empowered by Its powers.

17:31.190 --> 17:34.050
The Spirit exists; It has Its own powers.

17:34.170 --> 17:38.000
But we haven’t felt those powers within us.

17:38.100 --> 17:40.230
Once we feel the powers of the Spirit,

17:41.080 --> 17:45.200
we are empowered by our own powers which are there.

17:46.070 --> 17:49.020
The powers are within us.

17:49.150 --> 17:51.050
These are our own powers.

17:51.160 --> 17:53.190
We don’t have to borrow from anyone, ask from anyone,

17:54.060 --> 17:55.050
they are in ourselves.

17:55.180 --> 17:57.030
The Spirit is within us –

17:57.120 --> 18:01.100
only thing that Spirit has to bring light in our,

18:02.050 --> 18:05.170
in our consciousness.

18:06.020 --> 18:08.100
It has to come in our consciousness.

18:08.210 --> 18:12.150
In simple medical terminology we can see, say that the

18:12.220 --> 18:19.220
Spirit must manifest Itself in our central nervous system,

18:20.050 --> 18:23.010
in our central nervous system so that we should know

18:23.130 --> 18:24.190
what we are doing.

18:25.040 --> 18:29.090
Not that we start just jumping on the chair, or some

18:29.190 --> 18:32.190
people said, “Oh you, we just start doing it.”

18:33.050 --> 18:35.140
It is hypnosis.

18:35.140 --> 18:38.010
It’s not correct. You’re not in conscious mind.

18:38.100 --> 18:40.090
You are doing it out of hypnosis.

18:40.200 --> 18:44.020
Hypnosis may be coming from outside force.

18:44.020 --> 18:46.230
It’s not your force, your awareness,

18:47.070 --> 18:49.150
your understanding, your power.

18:50.020 --> 18:54.070
It is somebody else’s because you’re not doing it.

18:55.070 --> 18:58.190
As matter has a power to overpower us, in the same way

18:59.030 --> 19:03.020
there are some material things, I should say, which are

19:03.080 --> 19:05.200
very dangerous, which are placed.

19:06.070 --> 19:08.110
For example now cancer, take cancer,

19:08.190 --> 19:10.100
cancer overpowers.

19:10.160 --> 19:11.220
It’s a very serious thing.

19:12.110 --> 19:14.160
Cancer overpowers you; you cannot overpower cancer.

19:15.010 --> 19:16.160
Take a very concrete example.

19:17.000 --> 19:18.150
Now how is it caused?

19:19.000 --> 19:20.050
Doctors say this way, that way.

19:21.020 --> 19:23.190
We, Sahaja Yoga can cure cancer, definitely a hundred

19:24.090 --> 19:26.060
percent it can cure, it has cured.

19:26.180 --> 19:27.220
Many Sahaj Yogis have cured cancer.

19:28.100 --> 19:30.160
How? Is very simple.

19:31.000 --> 19:33.040
That you become master of yourself and you master the

19:33.150 --> 19:35.030
disease also,

19:35.130 --> 19:37.170
you master everything.

19:39.080 --> 19:41.220
Because the master is within you,

19:42.050 --> 19:45.040
it has not come in your conscious mind is the only link is

19:45.150 --> 19:47.220
left, and when that happens Yoga takes place,

19:48.040 --> 19:50.080
union takes place.

19:50.220 --> 19:55.060
We should now completely keep ourselves limited to

19:56.100 --> 19:59.150
Self Realization, about God I’ll tell next time.

20:00.000 --> 20:03.180
Self-Realization means to bring your Spirit

20:04.050 --> 20:06.010
into your conscious mind.

20:06.110 --> 20:09.210
Now how cancer is caused? Let’s see here what happens.

20:10.070 --> 20:12.070
It is caused by left-sided activity.

20:13.000 --> 20:17.180
Now left sided activities are emotional traumas,

20:18.080 --> 20:22.010
emotional problems, emotional upheavals,

20:22.100 --> 20:26.070
emotional insecurities – any kind of insecurity can take

20:26.180 --> 20:28.230
you to the left side.

20:29.090 --> 20:31.100
Little more movement can be these horrible gurus

20:31.190 --> 20:33.000
because they hypnotize you.

20:33.170 --> 20:35.070
They put you to the left.

20:35.070 --> 20:37.130
They put some spirit in you or I don’t know what they do,

20:37.240 --> 20:39.170
but they put you to the left.

20:40.000 --> 20:43.130
Any one of these activities which are not authorized by

20:43.190 --> 20:46.170
God, taken to, you go to the left side,

20:47.010 --> 20:49.080
because you cannot ascend in the center.

20:49.180 --> 20:51.140
So either you go to the left or to the right.

20:51.220 --> 20:55.100
When you overdo these things, like black magic - you

20:55.200 --> 20:58.090
have another thing here I’ve heard,

21:01.010 --> 21:04.010
some sort of a organization had, and the fellow you see

21:04.090 --> 21:07.060
he used to, everything he saw moving in the house.

21:07.140 --> 21:12.000
He came to Sahaj Yoga and his water jug was moving

21:12.120 --> 21:14.100
there and this was moving there and he couldn’t explain

21:14.180 --> 21:15.190
what was happening in his room.

21:16.070 --> 21:17.180
He was sitting down and he found something moving

21:18.040 --> 21:20.050
from here to here. It happens.

21:20.190 --> 21:23.120
What is that? What is that doing this kind of a thing

21:23.220 --> 21:24.230
which you cannot control.

21:25.130 --> 21:27.040
Again we come to the same point –

21:27.160 --> 21:28.220
something you cannot control.

21:29.060 --> 21:32.120
So you enter into the realm, into the realm

21:32.190 --> 21:36.120
where you are controlled and you are not under your own

21:36.210 --> 21:40.030
control and that realm, when you enter in,

21:40.030 --> 21:43.090
I have always seen all the cancer patients

21:43.170 --> 21:47.050
are the ones affected by this.

21:47.150 --> 21:51.060
Most of them. They’re not aware;

21:51.160 --> 21:53.090
they do not know how they get into it.

21:53.160 --> 21:56.160
For a lady, supposing, say she’s suffering from an

21:56.160 --> 22:00.150
insecurity about her husband or maybe something, or

22:00.240 --> 22:03.150
maybe she thinks that her husband may leave her any time.

22:03.230 --> 22:06.140
She loves him. Whatever it is,

22:07.010 --> 22:11.000
such a woman might get a breast cancer,

22:11.090 --> 22:13.230
because the insecurities set in, in one of the centers there

22:14.120 --> 22:17.230
which you can see here, the center of the Heart -

22:18.100 --> 22:20.130
Center heart, as we call it.

22:20.210 --> 22:25.000
Now if this center goes out of order,

22:25.080 --> 22:28.040
if a woman feels insecure for anything whatsoever,

22:28.170 --> 22:32.090
she’s capable – she’s vulnerable to be attacked and she

22:32.150 --> 22:35.090
can get into cancer.

22:35.230 --> 22:38.150
So we have to understand life in totality,

22:39.010 --> 22:41.050
and not in one way.

22:41.140 --> 22:45.120
The total impact of life, the total effect of life,

22:45.210 --> 22:50.160
the total relationship with life must be understood.

22:50.240 --> 22:53.070
Now no doctor knows this.

22:53.150 --> 22:56.230
Will he know, when he treats the patient for, say,

22:57.060 --> 23:02.240
breast cancer will he know that this lady is insecure?

23:03.210 --> 23:05.180
There’s another disease – anorexia –

23:06.010 --> 23:09.130
many girls suffer from it.

23:09.240 --> 23:12.000
They don’t just eat. They just give up eating.

23:12.200 --> 23:16.080
Now, you do not know why it happens.

23:16.160 --> 23:18.130
Doctors can’t cure it; nobody can cure it.

23:18.200 --> 23:20.010
What is the reason?

23:20.090 --> 23:24.120
The relationship of a girl, of a daughter with the father.

23:24.230 --> 23:28.000
Say father dies and the daughter doesn’t see the father,

23:28.110 --> 23:33.020
or in heart she loves the father but she doesn’t express it,

23:33.110 --> 23:36.090
or there’s some bad relationship that comes between the

23:36.170 --> 23:39.150
father and the daughter,

23:39.240 --> 23:41.240
you get this trouble – anorexia.

23:42.090 --> 23:46.190
You’ll be amazed but it is impossible for doctors to get –

23:47.040 --> 23:48.230
we have some doctors sitting here –

23:49.100 --> 23:54.040
it is impossible for any medical science to go near it.

23:56.020 --> 24:00.040
Because we do not see a human being in its totality.

24:00.140 --> 24:03.190
It’s a very delicate instrument God has created.

24:04.050 --> 24:05.210
The way we are harsh with others,

24:06.070 --> 24:11.000
the way we sometimes try to trouble others,

24:12.150 --> 24:17.220
try to make others feel insecured or unfair, unjust.

24:19.000 --> 24:21.140
Without our knowledge we really give them

24:22.110 --> 24:26.190
a tremendous insecurity, and such insecurities can

24:27.040 --> 24:34.030
work out incurable diseases of which we are not aware.

24:34.170 --> 24:38.170
So to understand the totality, what should happen to us?

24:39.040 --> 24:41.150
We should achieve that state where we can see

24:42.070 --> 24:44.060
the totality.

24:44.160 --> 24:48.130
Like if I have to see now, for example, the whole of

24:49.060 --> 24:51.090
Brighton, what should I do?

24:51.170 --> 24:54.230
I should go on a plane and see it from that height.

24:55.070 --> 24:58.150
I can see the whole. In the same way in your awareness,

24:58.230 --> 25:02.000
in your understanding, you should rise to that point from

25:02.080 --> 25:05.120
where you can see the whole.

25:05.210 --> 25:10.080
If you cannot see the whole, the partial vision, or we can

25:10.160 --> 25:16.170
say, a little that you see can create confusion,

25:16.240 --> 25:22.130
can create problems and some of them could be of a

25:22.210 --> 25:25.090
very, very serious nature.

25:25.190 --> 25:31.010
Because as human beings, we do not know what are we.

25:32.090 --> 25:36.100
This is the greatest problem of human beings,

25:36.180 --> 25:39.020
that they’ll say, “I don’t like it.”

25:39.110 --> 25:42.240
Now which one is this “I”? Is that your Spirit, or is that

25:43.080 --> 25:45.110
your ego?

25:45.210 --> 25:47.150
What is the part that is not liking it?

25:48.000 --> 25:50.160
Or is it your conditioning, because you’re brought up in a

25:51.000 --> 25:53.190
particular way so you don’t like this?

25:54.060 --> 25:57.160
Which part of you is not liking it?

25:58.020 --> 26:02.030
And you’d be amazed that it is not your Spirit because if

26:02.140 --> 26:06.100
Spirit likes, how will you know?

26:06.190 --> 26:08.230
It’s only through your vibrations.

26:09.080 --> 26:12.130
When you can feel the vibrations, then only you will say,

26:12.220 --> 26:14.030
“Yes, my Spirit likes it”,

26:14.200 --> 26:17.160
because the vibrations have emitted.

26:18.010 --> 26:22.010
So we are still in a transition state as human beings.

26:22.130 --> 26:26.050
We have not achieved that state which is called as the

26:26.130 --> 26:31.020
state of Self-Realization where you become the Spirit -

26:31.120 --> 26:33.120
the becoming is the point.

26:33.230 --> 26:38.020
Where you become the Spirit you know what you like.

26:38.100 --> 26:42.010
You really know what you really like,

26:42.140 --> 26:45.030
because you are now the reality,

26:45.130 --> 26:47.230
you are not any conditioning,

26:48.100 --> 26:52.150
you are no more an ego, but you are what you are really,

26:52.240 --> 26:54.220
and that is your Spirit.

26:55.070 --> 26:58.100
And, surprisingly this Spirit is a collective being.

26:58.210 --> 27:02.220
Is no artificial collectivity within us.

27:03.080 --> 27:05.130
That also “All right, we belong to all Brighton so we are

27:05.200 --> 27:09.080
one” or “We belong to one street so we are one.”

27:09.160 --> 27:12.210
It’s not like that, but is something that you are,

27:13.060 --> 27:15.190
absolutely you are a collective being,

27:16.020 --> 27:18.190
and you start feeling that collectivity within you

27:19.040 --> 27:21.150
with these different centers working it out.

27:22.010 --> 27:25.010
And you can feel it - others,

27:25.130 --> 27:27.100
you can feel others on your finger tips.

27:27.160 --> 27:28.200
Can you believe?

27:29.030 --> 27:32.150
In the Bible it’s written that your hands will speak.

27:33.160 --> 27:36.160
The description of these days is that your hands will speak.

27:36.230 --> 27:38.200
Why not people go and find out how does it happen?

27:39.060 --> 27:40.160
How can your hands speak?

27:40.240 --> 27:43.220
This is what happens that on your finger tips you start

27:44.060 --> 27:48.140
feeling and understanding what is reality,

27:48.200 --> 27:53.040
what is beauty, what is joy, what is love.

27:56.000 --> 27:58.060
This is the left side

27:58.160 --> 28:03.000
which we get, and ultimately with this left side problems

28:03.080 --> 28:05.240
we get physical pain.

28:06.070 --> 28:09.170
It’s very painful to have left sided problems –

28:10.000 --> 28:11.120
it’s very, very painful.

28:11.200 --> 28:14.220
The pain cannot be explained, no one can understand,

28:15.090 --> 28:18.010
nobody can cure it, you can’t tell anyone

28:18.120 --> 28:21.160
and people think that you are fussing, they give you

28:21.240 --> 28:24.170
psychological treatment, you just don’t understand

28:25.000 --> 28:27.020
why this pain is within you.

28:27.080 --> 28:29.200
And this pain comes to you from left side,

28:30.020 --> 28:32.090
the subconscious.

28:32.150 --> 28:34.110
But beyond the subconscious is the collective

28:34.190 --> 28:36.080
subconscious,

28:36.190 --> 28:40.030
and this collective subconscious is the one where

28:40.090 --> 28:47.030
whatever is created from the beginning up to today

28:47.100 --> 28:51.090
in the creation is within. And once you go to the

28:51.160 --> 28:54.150
subconscious, you just get lost there.

28:55.000 --> 28:58.080
You are so overpowered by this power of subconscious

28:58.190 --> 29:03.070
that it is beyond you to understand it,

29:03.140 --> 29:08.090
beyond you to get out of it and beyond you to –

29:08.210 --> 29:10.130
not to succumb to it.

29:10.210 --> 29:12.160
And it goes on increasing.

29:12.230 --> 29:14.070
Like I asked some people,

29:14.140 --> 29:17.100
“Why did you go on doing it when you knew that you

29:17.200 --> 29:20.000
were not doing it, somebody else was doing it?

29:20.080 --> 29:22.030
Still why did you continue to do it?”

29:22.120 --> 29:24.080
They said, “Mother, we were under the blanket,

29:24.180 --> 29:26.190
it was darkness, we didn’t know where we were moving

29:27.050 --> 29:30.050
and were just going on and on and on.”

29:30.130 --> 29:33.160
And as I told you last time, feeling guilty is the biggest

29:34.010 --> 29:35.170
blockade.

29:35.240 --> 29:38.130
Is the biggest blockade because once you start feeling

29:38.230 --> 29:43.030
guilty that this center on the left gets blocked and the –

29:43.160 --> 29:45.200
it’s very difficult.

29:46.030 --> 29:48.100
And you don’t know why you are feeling guilty.

29:48.170 --> 29:50.140
All the time you’re feeling guilty but you don’t know

29:50.210 --> 29:53.210
why you’re feeling guilty, why these ideas of guilt are

29:54.040 --> 29:57.130
coming to you, that this feeling of guilt keeps you away

29:57.210 --> 30:01.010
from joy, from enjoying anything, from being

30:01.150 --> 30:03.100
spontaneous.

30:03.100 --> 30:10.000
Why? And this explains why we sometimes are

30:10.070 --> 30:12.050
miserable for nothing at all.

30:12.160 --> 30:15.030
Actually, God has not created us to be miserable.

30:15.200 --> 30:18.140
He has made us so beautifully, so carefully.

30:19.040 --> 30:23.180
He has created us with such love and compassion,

30:24.020 --> 30:27.190
not to make us feel miserable, not for anything.

30:28.010 --> 30:31.030
He doesn’t give us any diseases, no problems.

30:31.140 --> 30:34.230
But we have done these things to ourselves by going to

30:35.070 --> 30:37.130
extremes on the left or the right.

30:37.210 --> 30:40.000
As I am today talking about only on the left,

30:40.120 --> 30:43.160
I would say that to feel miserable for nothing at all is

30:44.020 --> 30:48.120
also wrong, is being unjust to yourself.

30:48.230 --> 30:52.070
The people who are left sided must know that they are

30:52.130 --> 30:57.120
the Spirit, that they are that beauty which has to come,

30:57.220 --> 30:59.100
which has to express itself.

30:59.200 --> 31:03.110
That they are not the people who have to suffer

31:03.190 --> 31:07.090
all the time and to live like miserable people.

31:07.160 --> 31:09.010
They are not.

31:09.110 --> 31:12.010
But because they take so much upon themselves,

31:12.090 --> 31:15.160
bear so much upon themselves, they become like that.

31:15.240 --> 31:19.130
And to avoid that bearing up they may take to some other

31:20.010 --> 31:22.050
habits, you see. Many people take to alcohol

31:22.130 --> 31:26.130
also for reason because they can’t bear the pangs of life,

31:26.220 --> 31:29.110
they can’t bear it. That’s why they take to it …

31:29.190 --> 31:32.030
but once the Spirit is awakened within you,

31:32.110 --> 31:36.090
you become so strong. You become so joyous,

31:36.180 --> 31:40.010
so spontaneous that all these things drop out,

31:40.090 --> 31:43.180
all those things – so-called diseases, so-called habits -

31:44.040 --> 31:45.110
just drop out

31:46.080 --> 31:49.190
and you become a new, blooming personality.

31:51.060 --> 31:57.120
Now the basics of having this center within you –

31:58.070 --> 32:01.070
you can blame God for that, “Why did He give us these

32:01.130 --> 32:03.160
centers on the left hand side, what was the need?

32:03.230 --> 32:05.230
He should not have given these left sided ones, so we

32:06.050 --> 32:08.100
would have been just in the center to go.”

32:08.170 --> 32:13.010
But the trouble is the human beings have to know

32:13.080 --> 32:16.210
in their own freedom, how to deal with themselves.

32:17.040 --> 32:20.240
They have to learn little hard way the wisdom.

32:21.050 --> 32:23.040
They have to learn by going to extremes

32:23.160 --> 32:27.120
they have suffered. They have to realize it

32:27.200 --> 32:33.050
because if they have to become truly, absolutely free

32:34.000 --> 32:38.140
they have to rise in their wisdom.

32:38.210 --> 32:42.170
If they’re not wise people, then they cannot enter into the

32:43.000 --> 32:45.050
Kingdom of God, because they’ll be abandoned people.

32:45.180 --> 32:48.240
Say, people who are abandoned, who don’t understand

32:49.070 --> 32:51.210
any laws or regulations, if you get them in England,

32:52.050 --> 32:54.100
we’ll have to put them in jail.

32:54.200 --> 32:58.030
In the same way, human beings who have not got that

32:58.100 --> 33:00.240
wisdom within themselves –

33:01.090 --> 33:03.160
through sufferings only one learns, but we should not ask

33:04.040 --> 33:07.060
for suffering. When we ask for sufferings, we are asking

33:07.130 --> 33:09.190
actually for mistakes to begin with.

33:10.000 --> 33:12.000
How will you suffer if you do not commit mistakes?

33:12.140 --> 33:14.190
So, when we ask for sufferings we are committing

33:15.030 --> 33:16.080
mistakes.

33:16.210 --> 33:19.150
So what we should ask for is nothing but our Spirit,

33:20.000 --> 33:21.240
and if you ask for your Spirit,

33:22.070 --> 33:24.090
it is your own and you have to get it.

33:24.210 --> 33:28.080
It is in your own right that you’re going to get it.

33:28.230 --> 33:31.110
It’s no way that I’m obliging you or doing something

33:31.190 --> 33:33.170
special for you. It’s all there.

33:34.000 --> 33:36.200
You are like a light which is just to be enlightened

33:37.040 --> 33:40.210
because I’m an enlightened light and you become an

33:41.060 --> 33:43.240
enlightened light, you can enlighten other lights also.

33:44.090 --> 33:46.060
It’s very simple.

33:46.060 --> 33:47.190
If you become an enlightened light,

33:48.030 --> 33:49.060
you can enlighten others.

33:49.140 --> 33:50.210
You don’t have to bother about anything else then.

33:51.110 --> 33:55.050
You become an enlightened light yourself, that’s the point.

33:55.130 --> 33:59.100
It is all there, it is all your own, you have to just have it.

33:59.180 --> 34:05.170
It is as simple as that, there is nothing very complicated

34:05.230 --> 34:09.090
as these people make it or anything that these

34:09.090 --> 34:12.020
philosophers have put before you, nothing of the kind.

34:12.110 --> 34:16.080
It’s very simple, it is within you, it is spontaneous,

34:16.150 --> 34:19.120
it is a living process as in living process you have

34:19.120 --> 34:20.220
become human beings,

34:21.090 --> 34:22.230
you are going to become super human beings.

34:23.120 --> 34:26.060
It’s absolutely spontaneous, you can’t pay for it.

34:26.130 --> 34:29.040
How can you pay? I mean, absurd it is!

34:29.120 --> 34:34.170
If it is a living process, how can you pay?

34:34.230 --> 34:37.130
How much do you pay to the tree to grow up?

34:37.210 --> 34:40.210
I mean in anything living, do we pay anything?

34:40.210 --> 34:43.120
How much do we pay our nose to breathe?

34:43.180 --> 34:46.070
Can we pay for it? It’s absurd, it’s ridiculous.

34:46.160 --> 34:49.100
We cannot pay for it, we cannot, it’s a living process,

34:49.190 --> 34:54.000
you have to become, an egg has to become a chick.

34:54.090 --> 34:56.210
Now how much do you pay an egg to become a chick, or

34:57.020 --> 35:01.060
how much does the egg pay to the mother for becoming a

35:01.180 --> 35:02.170
chicken?

35:06.080 --> 35:10.080
It’s that ridiculous, but we never understand that living

35:10.150 --> 35:11.240
things are so spontaneous.

35:12.120 --> 35:14.170
We never see living things, we live with matter,

35:15.000 --> 35:17.150
we live with the dead, not with the living things.

35:17.240 --> 35:21.090
If you start watching a tree, you start watching a flower,

35:21.160 --> 35:24.060
how it becomes a fruit.

35:24.130 --> 35:27.080
You can’t even watch because it does it so slowly,

35:27.150 --> 35:30.020
you can’t even watch a flower becoming a fruit.

35:30.090 --> 35:32.160
Suddenly you find all coming up.

35:32.220 --> 35:37.110
Like when I came to London from India I found all the

35:37.110 --> 35:39.140
trees were bare,

35:39.230 --> 35:43.180
absolutely like dry sticks, absolutely like dry sticks.

35:44.030 --> 35:48.030
Within a week, what I find is the green coming up;

35:48.100 --> 35:50.090
and within second week it was all lush,

35:50.180 --> 35:52.060
you can’t believe it.

35:53.150 --> 35:56.060
We never even notice, we take it for granted.

35:56.170 --> 35:58.130
It’s happening. How does it happen?

35:58.230 --> 36:00.180
It’s a miraculous thing.

36:01.040 --> 36:03.070
If you see it, it’s miraculous how these flowers, for

36:03.130 --> 36:06.040
example the particular flowers are only on a particular

36:06.100 --> 36:09.030
tree and others, another, are on another tree.

36:09.110 --> 36:11.050
How does it happen?

36:11.140 --> 36:13.190
Who chooses them? Who puts them in proper shape?

36:13.190 --> 36:15.220
Who organizes all that?

36:16.050 --> 36:18.110
And this is what one has to realize and

36:18.180 --> 36:21.130
that is the All Pervading Power of God that does

36:22.000 --> 36:24.170
all the living work.

36:25.020 --> 36:28.200
And once you become that – the Spirit – then this power

36:29.020 --> 36:30.240
starts flowing through you.

36:31.050 --> 36:34.110
You feel the power through you as Christ was touched

36:34.190 --> 36:40.000
and He said some power has gone to someone, like that.

36:40.100 --> 36:43.120
You just become a medium of that power flowing.

36:43.230 --> 36:48.180
But you are empowered to maneuver it, to manage it,

36:48.240 --> 36:50.110
to understand it.

36:50.210 --> 36:52.160
You know completely about it, you know how to give it,

36:53.030 --> 36:56.000
you know to how to work it out, you know how to cure

36:56.150 --> 36:58.190
others, cure yourself.

36:59.090 --> 37:02.050
You know the complete working of your machinery.

37:02.160 --> 37:06.030
Apart from that, you get the powers to overcome all the

37:06.130 --> 37:10.090
problems of your own machinery also.

37:10.210 --> 37:12.110
It’s so fantastic.

37:12.210 --> 37:14.150
Whole thing sounds very fantastic because we have

37:14.240 --> 37:16.120
never seen this before.

37:16.240 --> 37:20.030
But to us it doesn’t sound fantastic when we see all these

37:20.120 --> 37:25.060
flowers suddenly turning into fruits. It doesn’t sound.

37:25.160 --> 37:28.220
But we see human beings turning into fruits,

37:29.070 --> 37:31.070
then it sounds very fantastic, “How can that be?”

37:31.180 --> 37:33.110
It has never happened before.

37:33.180 --> 37:36.060
Only one person would get Realization and it was such a

37:36.150 --> 37:38.140
difficult thing and nobody got it.

37:38.230 --> 37:41.000
How is it today?

37:41.220 --> 37:45.130
I say it is the blossom time which is been promised

37:45.230 --> 37:49.080
which is been already prophesized.

37:49.200 --> 37:53.070
Even a great poet in your country, William Blake,

37:53.190 --> 37:55.050
has prophesized it.

37:55.110 --> 37:58.040
He said these times will come when men of God will

37:58.110 --> 38:01.170
become prophets

38:02.010 --> 38:04.240
and these prophets will have power to make other

38:05.090 --> 38:07.090
prophets. I mean nobody could be more precise

38:07.220 --> 38:11.020
than Blake, I tell you. He was so great

38:11.120 --> 38:15.070
to say this will happen and this is what we have to expect

38:15.190 --> 38:17.140
when we go to anybody for seeking.

38:18.000 --> 38:21.000
Have we become prophets? And what is a prophet?

38:21.080 --> 38:23.230
Prophet is a person who is a collective being and

38:24.080 --> 38:29.020
who knows all about it, who is the master.

38:29.110 --> 38:31.220
We call prophet a master.

38:32.030 --> 38:34.160
And that’s what you have to become, the master.

38:35.020 --> 38:37.100
And that mastery is very simple because

38:37.170 --> 38:42.050
it’s all built within you, just it has to be connected.

38:42.160 --> 38:46.080
Like, anything like a television set is to be connected to

38:46.080 --> 38:49.040
the mains, it’s all built in, it’s there, it just starts working.

38:49.130 --> 38:53.060
In the same way, you are that, you are that.

38:53.160 --> 38:55.210
Just it is to be connected.

38:56.040 --> 38:59.000
Whatever may be your caste, community, race,

38:59.070 --> 39:03.060
nationality, shapes, heights – anything, whatever you

39:03.150 --> 39:06.060
may be – makes no difference because all of you have

39:06.190 --> 39:12.050
got this great thing within you, this power of a rebirth

39:12.160 --> 39:15.090
and you are to be born again, and you will be born again.

39:15.240 --> 39:19.020
Why not today?

39:19.170 --> 39:21.210
There’s nothing to get angry, because people get angry

39:22.050 --> 39:27.100
sometimes because they don’t like anybody telling them

39:27.200 --> 39:30.230
about something which of which they themselves are

39:31.060 --> 39:33.000
feeling bad.

39:33.140 --> 39:34.130
They don’t like it.

39:34.190 --> 39:36.240
For example if there’s a drunkard and he drinks too

39:37.110 --> 39:39.180
much, he’s an alcoholic, he doesn’t like it

39:40.040 --> 39:42.060
and he feels bad, and if somebody tells him,

39:42.160 --> 39:44.230
even in the most gentlest way that “You’d better give up

39:45.100 --> 39:47.240
drinking”, he doesn’t like it.

39:48.090 --> 39:52.020
But what I am saying is not that you should not do it,

39:52.120 --> 39:55.240
