Man: It seems very difficult the concept that Self

56:43.120 --> 56:46.240
Realization doesn’t involve some personal effort.

56:47.120 --> 56:53.020
Can it really come to anybody in effect of how

56:53.170 --> 56:58.010
materialistic they are? Am I understanding this?

56:59.070 --> 57:03.230
Yes, it appears on the face of it very difficult

57:04.110 --> 57:08.080
and how people are materialistic is also true no doubt,

57:08.190 --> 57:13.020
but Spirit is much stronger than the matter

57:13.090 --> 57:14.190
and when It has to express,

57:15.080 --> 57:20.240
It completely crushes all that and It comes.

57:21.070 --> 57:23.230
Now we have here, most of you are English people,

57:24.050 --> 57:26.240
I should say, westernized, very materialistic people they

57:27.070 --> 57:29.150
are there. I should say I mean living in that world,

57:29.230 --> 57:31.100
they may not have been that materialistic because if they

57:31.220 --> 57:35.040
are not seekers, they would not come to Me.

57:35.140 --> 57:38.170
But a new being has been born.

57:38.170 --> 57:40.090
If you look at an egg you feel,

57:40.180 --> 57:42.180
“Oh, what a hard stuff is this!”

57:43.200 --> 57:46.090
But if it is broken at the right moment,

57:46.160 --> 57:50.120
with the right understanding, it becomes a bird.

57:50.180 --> 57:54.040
Because a living process is all, only the last breakthrough

57:54.110 --> 57:55.200
has to take place.

57:56.090 --> 58:01.050
Apparently it looks difficult, but to Me it is not.

58:01.130 --> 58:04.070
Perhaps I know the job.

58:04.140 --> 58:06.030
All right?

58:09.220 --> 58:11.240
Yes, it looks … many people have said all kinds of

58:12.050 --> 58:13.150
things about Kundalini, also.

58:13.230 --> 58:16.070
I must say some books I have seen have horrified.

58:16.160 --> 58:18.090
You see if you don’t know the job, everything –

58:18.170 --> 58:20.180
supposing if somebody else doesn’t know how to drive a

58:21.020 --> 58:22.220
car, you see, and he gets into the car

58:23.070 --> 58:24.190
the way he’d describe it would be horrifying.

58:25.020 --> 58:28.100
You’d never get near a car, isn’t it? It’s like that.

58:28.180 --> 58:31.040
The one who is not authorized and does not know the job

58:31.120 --> 58:33.130
should not do it.

58:33.220 --> 58:37.120
But that’s what happens to you, that you become

58:37.200 --> 58:40.090
the Spirit, you become your own master

58:40.160 --> 58:43.030
and you become the master of this art –

58:43.090 --> 58:44.240
the master of this art.

58:45.050 --> 58:47.000
Yes, my child?

58:57.010 --> 58:58.020
I couldn't hear you?

59:02.180 --> 59:05.240
You mentioned hypnosis earlier and You also said that

59:06.080 --> 59:08.000
You regarded Yourself as a catalyst and

59:08.120 --> 59:13.150
don’t You think that the hypnotist also regards himself as

59:14.070 --> 59:15.000
a catalyst?

59:15.170 --> 59:18.000
Yes, Yes no doubt.

59:18.120 --> 59:21.110
Yes, yes that’s true, but the difference is this,

59:22.020 --> 59:25.140
that the hypnotist brings you under his power,

59:25.220 --> 59:29.010
he doesn’t give you any power or no dimension to your

59:29.070 --> 59:30.110
awareness - you see?

59:30.230 --> 59:33.110
There’s a tremendous difference between the two.

59:33.190 --> 59:36.110
You see, you have got your own power within you.

59:36.190 --> 59:39.090
Say, for example, all right, your Spirit there.

59:39.180 --> 59:42.190
Now I’m a catalyst, you see, you can use a spoon for

59:43.000 --> 59:47.240
giving a poison or could use it for giving a nectar,

59:48.060 --> 59:49.070
all right?

59:49.200 --> 59:53.040
So if you give the nectar, then it’s a great thing;

59:53.120 --> 59:56.170
and if you give the poison, it’s horrible. It’s like that.

59:56.170 --> 59:59.160
Now the hypnotist uses hypnosis –

59:59.240 --> 01:00:02.140
how does he hypnotize is the point.

01:00:02.210 --> 01:00:05.200
What he does is to push you into your subconscious,

01:00:06.030 --> 01:00:07.120
into your collective subconscious

01:00:07.200 --> 01:00:11.070
where he overpowers you. You are under his power.

01:00:11.150 --> 01:00:14.070
He says, “You become like a child”, you become like a child.

01:00:14.170 --> 01:00:16.020
“You suck a little bottle”, you do it.

01:00:16.020 --> 01:00:17.070
What’s all this?

01:00:17.160 --> 01:00:20.190
But here you become the Spirit in the sense that you

01:00:21.050 --> 01:00:23.050
become collectively conscious.

01:00:24.130 --> 01:00:28.100
It’s no hypnosis because you, yourself, can feel it.

01:00:28.200 --> 01:00:31.020
Now, say example you take ten children

01:00:31.110 --> 01:00:32.060
who are realized souls.

01:00:32.180 --> 01:00:34.100
There are some children who are realized souls,

01:00:34.210 --> 01:00:36.110
even little children.

01:00:36.230 --> 01:00:39.030
And you take them near a person who is suffering from

01:00:39.120 --> 01:00:41.030
some trouble, all right?

01:00:41.120 --> 01:00:43.210
Now you tie up their eyes and ask them,

01:00:44.060 --> 01:00:46.200
“What’s the problem of this gentleman?”

01:00:46.200 --> 01:00:49.090
They will raise the same fingers, all of them

01:00:49.220 --> 01:00:52.040
will raise the same fingers and say, “This is burning”,

01:00:52.100 --> 01:00:55.170
you see, because the sensation you feel – of burning,

01:00:55.240 --> 01:00:58.030
of numbness or of cool breeze,

01:00:59.160 --> 01:01:04.090
a new awareness of a vibratory nature is born within you.

01:01:04.180 --> 01:01:07.090
Not with hypnosis, on the contrary, after hypnosis you

01:01:07.170 --> 01:01:10.220
feel so tired and finished as if somebody has been riding

01:01:11.030 --> 01:01:13.160
your horse.

01:01:14.070 --> 01:01:15.160
It’s just the other way around.

01:01:16.050 --> 01:01:18.240
And you start growing into you and understanding,

01:01:19.080 --> 01:01:22.230
you can cure people you understand what are the centers

01:01:23.050 --> 01:01:24.070
that are catching,

01:01:24.170 --> 01:01:26.110
you understand what are the centers of another person

01:01:26.190 --> 01:01:27.240
that are catching.

01:01:28.100 --> 01:01:30.150
In the beginning sometimes people have confusion, I've seen,

01:01:30.220 --> 01:01:33.040
that they don’t know “whether these are my

01:01:33.130 --> 01:01:34.130
centers or your centers.”

01:01:34.240 --> 01:01:36.080
Now we have ways and methods by which you can

01:01:36.180 --> 01:01:37.180
discriminate.

01:01:38.010 --> 01:01:39.180
You can see which are your centers catching and which

01:01:40.010 --> 01:01:41.210
are the centers the other person catching.

01:01:42.060 --> 01:01:45.140
You also know how to get them all right,

01:01:45.200 --> 01:01:48.070
you also know how to give Realization to others,

01:01:48.160 --> 01:01:52.130
and to empower them with their own powers.

01:01:52.220 --> 01:01:55.140
It’s just the opposite.

01:01:55.210 --> 01:01:58.030
But catalyst could be horrifying,

01:01:58.100 --> 01:02:02.240
and catalyst could be just heavenly.

01:02:08.130 --> 01:02:11.140
Question: Can some people

01:02:12.060 --> 01:02:14.230
Self Realize themselves with their own effort?

01:02:15.080 --> 01:02:16.130
With their own effort?

01:02:17.240 --> 01:02:20.240
I don’t think it’s possible, you see, because

01:02:21.160 --> 01:02:24.240
like a light which is enlightened can only enlighten

01:02:25.070 --> 01:02:26.140
another light.

01:02:26.140 --> 01:02:31.110
But what I’m saying, that even supposing like Buddha,

01:02:31.180 --> 01:02:33.200
you see, He got His Realization when He was

01:02:34.040 --> 01:02:36.050
absolutely tired and He had to have it.

01:02:36.140 --> 01:02:38.140
Of course the Holy Ghost did that. He could not have

01:02:38.210 --> 01:02:39.230
done it on Him,

01:02:40.190 --> 01:02:44.180
but He got the Realization there because it was a

01:02:45.010 --> 01:02:47.180
different circumstance which He had to live,

01:02:48.020 --> 01:02:49.080
He didn’t have to talk about God,

01:02:49.210 --> 01:02:51.190
He didn’t have to talk about the whole thing,

01:02:52.060 --> 01:02:56.150
because people were so much engaged in talking of big

01:02:56.220 --> 01:03:01.100
things like God and about all kind of deities, this, that,

01:03:01.190 --> 01:03:03.070
there was a big confusion.

01:03:03.240 --> 01:03:06.030
And somebody was to be Realized at that time

01:03:06.110 --> 01:03:08.080
who would just localize it and say, “Only Self

01:03:08.180 --> 01:03:11.230
Realization – don’t talk of God or anything, forget it.”

01:03:12.070 --> 01:03:14.090
That’s why He got Realization like that.

01:03:14.210 --> 01:03:17.060
But you cannot get Realization just like that –

01:03:17.160 --> 01:03:21.090
only possession you can get. You cannot.

01:03:21.170 --> 01:03:24.100
Somebody who is an enlightened soul,

01:03:24.180 --> 01:03:28.130
such an enlightened soul doesn’t take money from you.

01:03:28.220 --> 01:03:31.120
Normally, you see, people don’t want to give you Relization -

01:03:31.190 --> 01:03:33.230
ninety-nine percent of those who are really realized,

01:03:34.070 --> 01:03:36.030
they’ll throw stones at you,

01:03:36.120 --> 01:03:38.040
they won’t have anything to do because their experiences

01:03:38.180 --> 01:03:40.080
of human beings are horrifying.

01:03:40.220 --> 01:03:43.100
If you go and talk to them, they’ll tell Me, they told Me

01:03:43.210 --> 01:03:45.040
that “Wait for twelve years.

01:03:45.120 --> 01:03:48.140
See, Mother, they will all finish You off, they’ll kill You,

01:03:48.240 --> 01:03:50.090
they’ll do this.”

01:03:50.180 --> 01:03:52.190
It’s very venturesome to deal with human beings because

01:03:53.020 --> 01:03:56.150
they’ll be very egoistical and they will never accept you.

01:03:57.000 --> 01:03:59.240
But if you take like this, like

01:04:02.110 --> 01:04:07.060
somebody who knows is a help, isn’t it?

01:04:07.230 --> 01:04:12.160
And Realization is not possible, is not possible to be

01:04:13.010 --> 01:04:15.090
done by yourself.

01:04:15.190 --> 01:04:19.200
It’s not possible, because if a, say, a candle which is not

01:04:20.050 --> 01:04:22.070
enlightened wants to get itself enlightened,

01:04:22.140 --> 01:04:25.210
the light has to be brought, isn’t it?

01:04:26.050 --> 01:04:27.220
It’s so simple like that.

01:04:28.050 --> 01:04:30.200
But one should not feel bad about it, actually.

01:04:30.200 --> 01:04:33.160
See, I don’t know how to drive, somebody drove Me down here.

01:04:33.230 --> 01:04:37.190
I didn’t feel bad that he had to drive Me down, did I?

01:04:38.060 --> 01:04:39.190
And I only know one job.

01:04:40.000 --> 01:04:40.180
I don’t know many.

01:04:40.240 --> 01:04:42.120
Many jobs I don’t know, I don’t know how to operate

01:04:42.180 --> 01:04:44.030
bank, I don’t know how to write a check,

01:04:44.120 --> 01:04:46.200
I’m hopeless in many things.

01:04:47.180 --> 01:04:50.010
I don’t know how to open a can, maybe.

01:04:50.100 --> 01:04:53.100
But I know how to open the Kundalini. All right?

01:04:53.190 --> 01:04:56.020
So if I know one job, why should you mind?

01:04:56.020 --> 01:05:00.100
After all, we depend on each other for everything, isn't it?

01:05:00.160 --> 01:05:03.120
So why not, if I know the job, what’s the harm?

01:05:03.210 --> 01:05:06.110
And you will know, too.

01:05:06.210 --> 01:05:08.040
You will know, too.

01:05:08.130 --> 01:05:10.200
But it cannot be done by yourself.

01:05:11.050 --> 01:05:15.230
But actually in this you’re not obliged for anything.

01:05:18.090 --> 01:05:21.060
I just do it because I love it.

01:05:21.140 --> 01:05:23.100
It’s just emits, I don’t do anyway, I’m just flowing,

01:05:24.000 --> 01:05:29.090
I don’t know how it happens, just it’s flowing.

01:05:35.020 --> 01:05:37.080
I just love for love’s sake.

01:05:37.230 --> 01:05:39.160
You can’t believe such a person can exist,

01:05:40.050 --> 01:05:42.210
but I do really, I am like that.

01:05:43.090 --> 01:05:45.130
Sometimes you might even, some of the Sahaja Yogis

01:05:45.210 --> 01:05:48.220
do feel that I’m too compassionate and that I should be

01:05:49.030 --> 01:05:51.090
rather strict with people and things like that, you see.

01:05:51.170 --> 01:05:55.180
They come and tell Me some wisdom about it.

01:05:59.120 --> 01:06:01.190
You see they think I’m not so practical,

01:06:02.040 --> 01:06:05.100
but this is the most practical thing.

01:06:06.020 --> 01:06:09.010
Yes, I know they make mistakes because they

01:06:09.010 --> 01:06:10.200
don't know they are walking in darkness.

01:06:11.020 --> 01:06:13.160
If you are walking in darkness, you will bang at something.

01:06:14.000 --> 01:06:15.210
Then only thing you can do is to have compassion for

01:06:16.060 --> 01:06:20.210
them because they can’t see, they are blind. Isn’t it?

01:06:21.040 --> 01:06:25.040
How can you have any anger or temper?

01:06:34.230 --> 01:06:37.170
And moreover, I would request you not to have any

01:06:38.010 --> 01:06:41.000
misidentification with anyone whatsoever.

01:06:41.060 --> 01:06:44.140
You have to get to your Spirit, that’s the main thing.

01:06:44.240 --> 01:06:47.120
If you still think of somebody, you see,

01:06:47.220 --> 01:06:49.140
like the lady – I don’t know, somebody might have sent

01:06:49.230 --> 01:06:52.070
her here, maybe. I don’t know why she got angry.

01:06:52.130 --> 01:06:54.200
I didn’t say anything to hurt her.

01:06:54.200 --> 01:06:55.230
May be she is possessed.

01:06:55.230 --> 01:06:59.000
I don’t know why she has got angry with Me,

01:06:59.090 --> 01:07:01.070
and she just got up and just walked off saying that

01:07:01.130 --> 01:07:03.020
“You’re telling everything lies.”

01:07:05.100 --> 01:07:07.110
Why should I tell you lies?

01:07:07.200 --> 01:07:10.170
I don’t have to get anything out of you.

01:07:12.180 --> 01:07:14.000
But why it happens?

01:07:14.000 --> 01:07:15.200
Because she’s not sensitive,

01:07:16.040 --> 01:07:19.030
she’s not sensitive to Divinity.

01:07:20.090 --> 01:07:22.040
She doesn’t understand who’s Divine, who’s...

01:07:22.220 --> 01:07:25.110
I don’t blame her.

01:07:25.210 --> 01:07:27.140
She hasn’t got the sensitivity. It’s a caliber.

01:07:27.230 --> 01:07:30.060
I have seen Sahaja Yogis now of different varieties

01:07:30.130 --> 01:07:31.170
have come to Me.

01:07:32.000 --> 01:07:34.150
Some of them are of such a caliber you can’t even believe.

01:07:34.220 --> 01:07:36.100
They get into Realization, they know what it is,

01:07:36.210 --> 01:07:38.090
they have the pattern just like a diamond,

01:07:38.180 --> 01:07:40.030
they get it and they get to it.

01:07:40.150 --> 01:07:42.130
They’re tremendous people.

01:07:42.240 --> 01:07:45.080
There are some who slog behind.

01:07:45.140 --> 01:07:51.010
Some of them who get Realization but still

01:07:51.200 --> 01:07:54.010
they go on doubting. All kinds.

01:07:54.090 --> 01:07:58.150
Doesn’t matter. I love all of them.

01:08:00.110 --> 01:08:02.020
Yes, my child?

01:08:18.230 --> 01:08:21.030
He is a Sahaja yogi?

01:08:35.180 --> 01:08:38.150
If before Realization we were such a horrible person that

01:08:39.000 --> 01:08:41.070
we gave cancer to everybody we met or something like

01:08:41.150 --> 01:08:47.020
this, after Realization does the effects of that get taken

01:08:47.090 --> 01:08:49.050
away, or what happens?

01:08:49.150 --> 01:08:53.030
Yah. I know it, so many things have happened.

01:08:53.120 --> 01:08:56.110
We had somebody in Brighton, you remember –

01:08:56.210 --> 01:08:59.010
he’s here right now, I think –

01:09:00.120 --> 01:09:02.070
who was drunk when he came in.

01:09:02.160 --> 01:09:04.140
He was very angry with Me, you see, to begin with.

01:09:04.220 --> 01:09:06.150
He said, “How can I get rid of this trouble?

01:09:06.220 --> 01:09:08.090
I can’t believe You”, and all that.

01:09:08.190 --> 01:09:10.170
And he’s all right, perfectly all right.

01:09:11.000 --> 01:09:14.130
His change is so beautiful, you can’t… is he there?

01:09:14.130 --> 01:09:15.080
Yogi: Yes , I am.

01:09:15.160 --> 01:09:17.210
May God bless you.

01:09:21.180 --> 01:09:22.180
He’s so sweet now.

01:09:23.030 --> 01:09:25.090
The other day he came to see Me.

01:09:26.130 --> 01:09:28.230
I said, “Look at that. He’s so sweet.”

01:09:29.080 --> 01:09:31.190
He was a very sweet man, wasn’t he?

01:09:32.040 --> 01:09:36.160
But something had put him up, made him upset, you see,

01:09:37.010 --> 01:09:39.110
that he became alcoholic, you see.

01:09:39.210 --> 01:09:41.130
He’s all right.

01:09:42.040 --> 01:09:45.140
The compassion can only make you understand that

01:09:45.230 --> 01:09:47.160
there’s a reason for this –

01:09:48.070 --> 01:09:52.040
He is a very sweet person, very sweet person no doubt.

01:09:52.240 --> 01:09:55.020
But something had gone wrong with him.

01:09:55.120 --> 01:09:57.120
It’s all right.

01:09:59.190 --> 01:10:01.180
So this happens, it’s true.

01:10:03.110 --> 01:10:05.040
Sahaja Yogis realize this.

01:10:05.130 --> 01:10:09.030
Some, of course, I must say, go little bit.

01:10:09.100 --> 01:10:12.140
Doesn’t matter. They’ll come up, all of them will come,

01:10:12.230 --> 01:10:15.160
I’m sure of it.

01:10:18.040 --> 01:10:21.240
Everyone is made for it.

01:10:22.090 --> 01:10:25.040
Actually, the Divine is anxious to give you Realization –

01:10:25.150 --> 01:10:29.110
much more, much more anxious than you are.

01:10:29.200 --> 01:10:31.080
If there were thousand people today,

01:10:31.190 --> 01:10:33.240
I would have given them Realization better.

01:10:34.110 --> 01:10:36.180
But very few people take to reality, you see now.

01:10:37.050 --> 01:10:39.150
That guru maharaji, thousands are like mad after him,

01:10:40.100 --> 01:10:42.110
isn’t it?

01:10:42.230 --> 01:10:46.120
He’s given nothing to the poor people.

01:10:47.100 --> 01:10:51.020
But for reality, there are very few.

01:10:53.100 --> 01:10:55.150
Like other day somebody asked Me a question,

01:10:56.000 --> 01:10:57.190
“Mother, why don’t You do it to everyone?”

01:10:58.050 --> 01:11:00.050
I said, “Where are they, everyone?

01:11:00.140 --> 01:11:03.070
They are busy. Where are they?

01:11:03.160 --> 01:11:06.200
In this Brighton, how many there are?

01:11:07.160 --> 01:11:09.200
How many are here?

01:11:10.040 --> 01:11:12.140
All right? That’s the problem.

01:11:12.240 --> 01:11:18.100
It takes time for people to love reality. Time.

01:11:18.210 --> 01:11:21.220
It’s such a beautiful thing.

01:11:22.070 --> 01:11:25.060
And even they get realized, then they drop out, you see.

01:11:25.140 --> 01:11:27.030
They say, “Oh, I’m all right now. I’m all right.”

01:11:27.130 --> 01:11:30.020
After one year they’ll appear.

01:11:30.110 --> 01:11:31.140
That’s not the way.

01:11:31.220 --> 01:11:34.160
You have to master this art, absolutely master it.

01:11:35.000 --> 01:11:37.150
It is all free, absolutely free.

01:11:37.230 --> 01:11:42.070
Now they are all sitting down here, they can say that.

01:11:43.220 --> 01:11:46.130
Would You talk a bit more about Self Realization and

01:11:47.030 --> 01:11:49.150
what’s necessary to enhance that.

01:11:50.140 --> 01:11:54.230
Yes, Yes, I will be in my next lecture, one by one.

01:11:55.100 --> 01:11:57.180
Now I’m talking the left side, the right side,

01:11:58.040 --> 01:12:00.130
and then the center, and then also, of course,

01:12:00.220 --> 01:12:01.190
about the Spirit.

01:12:02.040 --> 01:12:04.110
Definitely, hundred times, that’s what I have to do.

01:12:04.220 --> 01:12:07.100
But gradually I have to build you up. All right?

01:12:07.190 --> 01:12:09.020
I will definitely. You won’t believe,

01:12:11.240 --> 01:12:14.090
I think I have given five hundred lectures already

01:12:14.170 --> 01:12:17.190
in London, at least. And it doesn’t end.

01:12:18.020 --> 01:12:19.180
Every time, they say last time I spoke they said,

01:12:20.020 --> 01:12:21.210
“Mother it was absolutely a new dimension

01:12:22.070 --> 01:12:23.200
You talked about”, you see.

01:12:24.050 --> 01:12:26.000
I don’t know, Kerry told Me first time he touched his

01:12:26.090 --> 01:12:27.230
vibrations so much with my lecture

01:12:28.130 --> 01:12:31.160
I don’t know what I touched him so much.

01:12:31.230 --> 01:12:33.120
Yes, it’s surprising.

01:12:33.210 --> 01:12:35.150
He’s from Australia.

01:12:35.240 --> 01:12:40.070
Australians do well. Very fast work.

01:12:41.080 --> 01:12:44.080
So, all the questions are over now? Should we have it?

01:12:46.190 --> 01:12:48.040
What are karmas?

01:12:48.110 --> 01:12:55.070
Karmas are when you do any work or anything with your

01:12:55.130 --> 01:12:58.240
right side action then

01:13:00.050 --> 01:13:04.020
the effects of that accumulate within you as an ego

01:13:04.110 --> 01:13:05.200
because you think you are doing it.

01:13:06.060 --> 01:13:08.210
Actually, we don’t do anything substantial.

01:13:09.040 --> 01:13:11.190
What we do is a dead work like as I said we make a chair

01:13:12.010 --> 01:13:14.090
out of a dead, a tree.

01:13:14.150 --> 01:13:16.230
That’s all we do. What work we do is an idea we have

01:13:17.070 --> 01:13:18.060
we are doing work.

01:13:18.140 --> 01:13:19.140
What work are you doing?

01:13:20.030 --> 01:13:21.230
Can you convert this into a fruit?

01:13:22.060 --> 01:13:25.030
We can’t even put fragrance into it.

01:13:25.180 --> 01:13:28.210
So this myth, you see, works as ego within us as shown

01:13:29.040 --> 01:13:31.210
here, which I will be speaking tomorrow about, all right?

01:13:32.070 --> 01:13:34.200
And this is what is that we think we are doing this work,

01:13:35.020 --> 01:13:39.030
that work, and this ego thinks that if you have done bad

01:13:39.120 --> 01:13:42.240
work or good work we have to suffer.

01:13:43.110 --> 01:13:45.170
You see, a tiger doesn’t feel that way.

01:13:46.030 --> 01:13:48.200
If tiger has to eat, it must kill.

01:13:49.020 --> 01:13:51.220
It kills the animal, eats it, finished.

01:13:52.080 --> 01:13:54.180
It doesn’t sit down and sulk, “Oh, God, I shouldn’t have

01:13:55.020 --> 01:14:00.120
done it. I should become vegetarian.”

01:14:00.220 --> 01:14:05.040
It doesn’t accumulate any, any, any karmas in it,

01:14:05.120 --> 01:14:07.180
all right? But we human beings do. Why?

01:14:08.020 --> 01:14:10.030
Because we are closed.

01:14:10.120 --> 01:14:12.170
We are closed. See here, we are closed.

01:14:13.030 --> 01:14:14.050
They are open.

01:14:14.130 --> 01:14:16.060
Whatever they do, they are not bothered.

01:14:16.060 --> 01:14:18.070
But we are bothered about what we do

01:14:18.130 --> 01:14:20.140
because we think we do.

01:14:23.000 --> 01:14:27.080
And when, as I said, this center is opened out

01:14:27.170 --> 01:14:30.070
He sucks our karmas, and the so-called karmas are

01:14:30.150 --> 01:14:33.000
nothing but sins, you see –

01:14:33.100 --> 01:14:36.140
in a biblical language we can call it as sin, you see.

01:14:36.220 --> 01:14:39.110
And they’re all sucked in

01:14:40.200 --> 01:14:45.240
by this powerful Deity of Christ awakened within us.

01:14:45.240 --> 01:14:47.130
And you get beyond it because

01:14:47.210 --> 01:14:49.180
it is the ego that does the karma.

01:14:50.110 --> 01:14:53.090
When your ego is finished, where are the karmas?

01:14:53.170 --> 01:14:56.020
They are finished, too.

01:15:00.120 --> 01:15:02.220
Then you don’t say, “I did it.”

01:15:03.050 --> 01:15:06.050
What you will say, “Mother, it’s not working out.

01:15:06.150 --> 01:15:08.130
It’s not going up.” Now what is this “it” –

01:15:08.210 --> 01:15:11.200
it becomes a third person. “It’s flowing.

01:15:12.040 --> 01:15:13.100
The vibrations not coming.”

01:15:13.220 --> 01:15:16.190
You see, you don’t say, “I, I am doing this Realization.

01:15:17.030 --> 01:15:19.180
I am raising the kunda ..”, they don’t say so.

01:15:20.040 --> 01:15:25.110
They say, “It’s not rising.” You become a third person.

01:15:25.200 --> 01:15:27.220
That third person is the Spirit.

01:15:28.070 --> 01:15:31.050
Where you do not say that “I should do it.”

01:15:31.160 --> 01:15:33.030
Even if it’s your son, you say,

01:15:33.100 --> 01:15:35.050
“Mother, it’s better he gets Realization.”

01:15:35.150 --> 01:15:39.020
All right. You’ll see. Try it. It didn’t work out?

01:15:39.120 --> 01:15:41.220
All right, then should I give a certificate?

01:15:42.060 --> 01:15:43.110
He said, “How can You give certificate,

01:15:43.210 --> 01:15:46.080
Mother, how can anybody, Kundalini has not risen.”

01:15:46.160 --> 01:15:48.120
Everyone knows, you see, whether it’s your father,

01:15:48.210 --> 01:15:50.040
mother, sister - anyone –

01:15:50.140 --> 01:15:52.090
if they’re not realized, they know they’re not realized,

01:15:52.170 --> 01:15:56.190
so what. They just know.

01:15:57.220 --> 01:16:00.000
This granddaughter of Mine, who was …

01:16:00.070 --> 01:16:03.120
she’s here now, she is a born realized,

01:16:03.120 --> 01:16:05.100
and she was hardly about five years of age, I think,

01:16:05.170 --> 01:16:06.240
when they went to Ladakh.

01:16:07.200 --> 01:16:09.160
There was one lama sitting with a shaved head and all

01:16:09.230 --> 01:16:11.100
that, wearing and all that.

01:16:11.180 --> 01:16:14.000
Everybody was touching his feet, and the parents also

01:16:14.110 --> 01:16:16.230
not realized, my daughter is not realized, so she also

01:16:17.060 --> 01:16:18.000
touched his feet.

01:16:18.110 --> 01:16:19.140
She couldn’t bear it anymore now,

01:16:20.000 --> 01:16:20.180
it was too much for her.

01:16:21.090 --> 01:16:23.070
She was sitting in a higher block, she went,

01:16:24.020 --> 01:16:26.030
put her hands back and looked at him, you see, told him.

01:16:26.210 --> 01:16:29.010
She says, “What do you mean by asking everybody to

01:16:29.090 --> 01:16:33.030
touch your feet? You’re not a even a realized soul.

01:16:33.130 --> 01:16:36.020
By wearing this dress of yours and shaving your head

01:16:36.090 --> 01:16:39.060
you think you can ask people to touch your feet?”

01:16:39.140 --> 01:16:44.060
Little child of five years, yet she understands.

01:16:44.150 --> 01:16:47.120
We had once a program in India when they invited Me

01:16:47.200 --> 01:16:50.070
as a chief guest and for this Ramanmash?,

01:16:50.150 --> 01:16:54.020
she was a realized soul; and one gentleman from

01:16:54.110 --> 01:16:56.020
Ramkrishna ashram from the head of that was sitting

01:16:56.140 --> 01:17:01.070
with his big orange robe, you see, sitting there.

01:17:01.130 --> 01:17:03.040
And my, another granddaughter,

01:17:03.130 --> 01:17:05.010
she was sitting in the front row.

01:17:05.100 --> 01:17:06.130
She couldn’t bear him anymore

01:17:06.210 --> 01:17:08.030
so she shouted from there,

01:17:08.100 --> 01:17:12.050
“Mother, the one whose wearing a maxi dress,

01:17:12.120 --> 01:17:14.000
Grandmother, please ask him to get out,

01:17:14.080 --> 01:17:15.240
he’s giving heat to all of us.”

01:17:16.050 --> 01:17:17.180
So you see, there were many Sahaj Yogis who were

01:17:17.240 --> 01:17:19.150
feeling the heat from this fellow and he thinks he’s a

01:17:20.010 --> 01:17:20.240
very spiritual man.

01:17:21.100 --> 01:17:24.020
She said, “Ask him to go, he’s wearing a maxi.”

01:17:24.200 --> 01:17:26.200
She didn’t understand it was a robe or thing.

01:17:27.020 --> 01:17:29.080
Even children know

01:17:29.170 --> 01:17:31.220
who are realized souls and who are not,

01:17:32.050 --> 01:17:33.100
if they are born realized.

01:17:33.100 --> 01:17:35.130
There are many children who are born realized these days.

01:17:35.190 --> 01:17:40.000
The time of judgment, this is the time of judgment.

01:17:40.080 --> 01:17:42.240
Of course about this I’ll tell you later.

01:17:48.080 --> 01:17:50.090
Do You mind if I ask You a few questions?

01:17:50.210 --> 01:17:52.140
It’s all right, I don’t mind.

01:17:52.230 --> 01:17:54.100
But what happens, if you ask too many questions

01:17:54.190 --> 01:17:58.090
sometimes it becomes mental activity and may delay

01:17:58.190 --> 01:18:00.140
further Realization sometimes,

01:18:00.230 --> 01:18:03.150
so I would advice you, if it is not so important, better

01:18:03.240 --> 01:18:06.100
keep it out because, you see, answering the question is

01:18:06.190 --> 01:18:08.020
only on mental level.

01:18:08.110 --> 01:18:10.040
I’m talking something much beyond, you see.

01:18:10.180 --> 01:18:14.010
So, it is something logically if you have understood Me -

01:18:14.080 --> 01:18:15.210
all right, let’s have it.

01:18:16.060 --> 01:18:17.240
If it will work out, work out. If it will not work out,

01:18:18.060 --> 01:18:19.020
doesn’t matter.

01:18:19.090 --> 01:18:22.180
I’m here for three-four days, and we are going to work it

01:18:23.020 --> 01:18:24.100
out. All right?

01:18:24.240 --> 01:18:26.160
So it’s better to keep your mind at rest. Tell the mind,

01:18:27.020 --> 01:18:28.210
“You have asked many questions before,

01:18:29.140 --> 01:18:32.200
you have thought of many things, now the time for you

01:18:33.100 --> 01:18:39.050
to receive the blessings of your own being.” All right?

01:18:39.150 --> 01:18:41.000
If you tell your mind, it will rest.

01:18:41.180 --> 01:18:44.170
It’s a, it’s a wonderful thing mind is.

01:18:45.010 --> 01:18:50.030
If the mind knows what you want, and if it is the reality,

01:18:50.120 --> 01:18:53.060
it supports you and helps you very much.

01:18:53.150 --> 01:18:56.080
The same mind which can go astray, you see,

01:18:56.160 --> 01:18:58.170
it’s like sometimes I say it’s like a donkey,

01:18:59.090 --> 01:19:04.130
like Christ used donkey just to suggest the mind

01:19:04.240 --> 01:19:10.140
that if you allow it to go astray it will take you to all

01:19:10.220 --> 01:19:14.050
kinds of things, but if you control it, it takes you there

01:19:14.120 --> 01:19:17.040
where you have to go.

01:19:17.190 --> 01:19:20.020
You just make him keep quiet.

01:19:20.100 --> 01:19:23.100
It’s better to keep quiet at mind level.

01:19:23.190 --> 01:19:26.050
And that’s why I answered your questions because later

01:19:26.160 --> 01:19:29.090
on when the Kundalini’s rising, at that time,

01:19:29.190 --> 01:19:31.160
the mind should not stand up, isn’t it, to say that

01:19:32.010 --> 01:19:34.050
“I haven’t asked this question.” That’s why.

01:19:34.130 --> 01:19:36.090
Just to soothe it – there’s no need –

01:19:36.180 --> 01:19:39.230
but, just to soothe it down, I do it. All right?

01:19:40.070 --> 01:19:42.090
So best thing is to get your Realization is the best thing,

01:19:42.170 --> 01:19:45.030
otherwise this mind is quite a disturbing stuff.

01:19:45.110 --> 01:19:47.160
It can come at the right time when you are going to

01:19:47.240 --> 01:19:52.100
achieve your last breakthrough, it may stop. All right?

01:19:52.170 --> 01:19:55.170
So if you have any immediate question by which you are

01:19:56.000 --> 01:19:57.170
really oppressed then you must ask Me.

01:19:58.040 --> 01:20:00.050
But if it is not so important, just give up.

01:20:00.120 --> 01:20:01.230
Is it very important?

01:20:01.230 --> 01:20:04.030
Then it’s all right. He has realized.
